content:
CRM Analytics prebuilt apps are ready-to-use applications that offer advanced analytics and reporting capabilities specifically tailored for sales and customer relationship management. The apps provide preconfigured dashboards, reports, and data visualizations to analyze business data.

The Einstein Accuracy Analytics Template helps you monitor how well Einstein Discovery models predict actual outcomes over time. Track subscription renewals with the Subscription Analytics App and configure-price-quote process with the Quoting Analytics App.

Get insights into deal pricing with the Pricing Analytics App, adoption analytics with the Adoption Analytics Template, and marketing performance with the Campaign Analytics App. Evaluate scheduling efficiency with the Appointment Analytics App and monitor object usage with the Change Analytics App.

Increase approval process visibility with the Approval Analytics App and trend data using the Snapshot Analytics App. Visualize sales data and opportunities with the Cluster Analysis Account Segmentation App.

The Service Analytics template gets you started fast with Analytics, providing a clear path through your Service Cloud data on any device. Get sales predictions with the Einstein Discovery for Sales Analytics App, ecommerce data insights with the B2B Commerce Analytics App, and customer service performance insights with the Social Case Analytics App.

Explore fundraising performance with the Fundraising Analytics App, measure impact with the Fundraising Performance Analytics App, and get a combined analysis of Sales and Service clouds with Customer Insights. Use the Multi Org Sales Analytics Template to create a scaled-down version of the Sales Analytics that pulls in data from all your connected orgs.

Sales Analytics brings the power of Analytics to Sales Cloud on any device that supports Analytics, providing intuitive visualizations based on your Salesforce data. Create an app from the Lead Trending Analytics Template or Pipeline Analytics Template for instant insights into your team's lead conversion process and pipeline snapshot data.
title: CRM Analytics Prebuilt Apps
